<Layout 
  title="AI-Powered Solutions for Small Businesses | Monsoft Solutions" 
  description="Help your small business compete with the big players. AI automation, local SEO, smart websites, and 24/7 AI assistants for contractors, salons, restaurants & more in Southwest Florida."
  structuredData={structuredData}
>
  <Header />
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container-narrow">
        <span class="hero-label reveal">Small Business Solutions</span>
        <h1 class="hero-title reveal reveal-delay-1">
          Big business technology.
          <span class="highlight">Small business pricing.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle reveal reveal-delay-2">
          You didn't start your business to spend all day on paperwork, missed calls, 
          and chasing leads. We use AI and automation to give you back your time‚Äîso 
          you can focus on what you actually love doing.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-cta reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">
            Get Your Free Consultation
