              <span class="stat-value" data-value={stat.value}>{stat.value}</span>
              <span class="stat-label">{stat.label}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Problem Section -->
    <section class="problem section-padding">
      <div class="container-wide">
        <div class="problem-grid">
          <div class="problem-content reveal">
            <span class="section-label">The Reality</span>
            <h2>Running a small business is hard enough</h2>
            <p>
              You're the owner, the marketer, the accountant, the customer service rep, and 
              sometimes the janitor. There's never enough time, and the big chains have 
              technology and budgets you can't match.
            </p>
            <p>
              But here's the thing: <strong>you don't need a Fortune 500 budget anymore.</strong> The same 
              AI and automation tools that power big businesses are now accessible to you‚Äî
              and we make them work without requiring a tech degree.
            </p>
