              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="problem-item">
              <span class="problem-icon">üëª</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Invisible Online</strong>
                <p>Customers search "near me" and find your competitors because your online presence is weak.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="problem-item">
