        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Value Proposition -->
    <section class="value-prop section-padding bg-dark">
      <div class="container-narrow">
        <div class="value-content reveal">
          <span class="section-label">Why Monsoft</span>
          <h2>We're local. We get it.</h2>
          <p>
            We're not some big agency that treats you like a number. We're a Southwest Florida 
            company that understands local business. We've seen what works here, we know 
            the challenges, and we build solutions that fit your budget.
          </p>
          <div class="value-points">
            <div class="value-point">
              <span class="value-icon">üè†</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Local Support</strong>
